{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-post-jsx","path":"/why-spekboom","webpackCompilationHash":"6915e087dec7788684e4","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"html":"<h2>How does it work?</h2>\n<ol>\n<li>Spekboom plantations in the Karoo of South Africa provide one of the most cost effective carbon offset solutions. </li>\n<li>We represent these plantations individually as always for sale NFTs. </li>\n<li>Holding an NFT continuously generates verifiable carbon credits (ERC20 tokens). </li>\n<li>Corporations can burn carbon credits to transparently showcase they are carbon neutral.</li>\n<li>The Harberger tax received from the entities holding the always for sale NFTs, flows directly to the farmers for income and the upkeep of the spekboom plantations. </li>\n</ol>","frontmatter":{"date":"2019-10-19","title":"How does carbon credits club work?","tags":["Carbon","Spekboom"],"cover":{"childImageSharp":{"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":1.680244399185336,"src":"/static/a9f8c6c6d79c9711b2ed34c44ec0d4a8/3c739/TheGreenWall.png","srcSet":"/static/a9f8c6c6d79c9711b2ed34c44ec0d4a8/4f634/TheGreenWall.png 480w,\n/static/a9f8c6c6d79c9711b2ed34c44ec0d4a8/3c739/TheGreenWall.png 825w","srcWebp":"/static/a9f8c6c6d79c9711b2ed34c44ec0d4a8/8d625/TheGreenWall.webp","srcSetWebp":"/static/a9f8c6c6d79c9711b2ed34c44ec0d4a8/bc3bf/TheGreenWall.webp 480w,\n/static/a9f8c6c6d79c9711b2ed34c44ec0d4a8/8d625/TheGreenWall.webp 825w","sizes":"(max-width: 825px) 100vw, 825px"},"resize":{"src":"/static/a9f8c6c6d79c9711b2ed34c44ec0d4a8/d8210/TheGreenWall.png"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"pathSlug":"/why-spekboom","prev":{"frontmatter":{"path":"/spekboom-carbon-credits-inspiration","title":"Why carbon credits?","tags":["Spekboom"]}},"next":null}}}